    "body": "`b:match_words` which contains patterns used by `matchit` plugin to find tag's counterpath, is fixed so that matching happens using the whole tag, not just its first letter.\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nis described in details in https://github.com/chrisbra/matchit/issues/51; in short: for htmls matching for tags happens using only first letter of the tag.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nuse whole tag",
